    <div class="vocab-item">
      <h2>Variable</h2>
      <p>A symbol, usually a letter, that represents a number in mathematical expressions or equations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="vocab-item">
      <h2>Equation</h2>
      <p>A mathematical statement that shows two expressions are equal, using the equal sign (=).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="vocab-item">
      <h2>Coefficient</h2>
      <p>The number that multiplies a variable in an algebraic expression.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="vocab-item">
      <h2>Expression</h2>
      <p>A combination of numbers, variables, and operations that represents a value.</p>
    </div>

